rypt</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">&nbsp;</code></pre>\n<h2>Deploy</h2>\n<h3>Sinkronisasi Repositori</h3>\n<h3>Buat Service NodeJS</h3>\n<h2>Backup</h2>\n<h3>Backup DB Dev</h3>\n<h1>SMART Live</h1>\n<h2>Connect</h2>\n<h3>Akses ke AWS</h3>\n<h3>Menyambungkan melalui SSH</h3>\n<h2>Prepare</h2>\n<h3>Install Dependency</h3>\n<h3>Install Database</h3>\n<h3>Buat Direktori API dan WEB</h3>\n<h3>Buat User Database MongoDB</h3>\n<h2>Deploy</h2>\n<h3>Sinkronisasi Dengan Repositori</h3>\n<h3>Restore Database</h3>\n<h3>Buat Service NodeJS</h3>\n<h3>Buat VirtualHost Apache2 dan aktifkan ssl let\'s encrypt</h3>\n<h2>Backup</h2>\n<h3>Buat Folder untuk backup</h3>\n<h3>Buat Bash File untuk backup API Upload Folder</h3>\n<h3>Buat Bash File untuk Backup Database</h3>\n<h3>Konfigurasi Crontab</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Common Issues</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','html','2021-09-01T03:32:51.630Z','ckeditor','en',1,'2021-08-31T09:48:15.097Z','{}'),(23,'projects/vfcs','dd02c02c7cd532df91466750b847a89ddbb5d3a4','VFCS Project','Describe how to access and manage',0,1,'','','updated',3,'<h1>Requirement</h1>\n<ol>\n  <li>Install MongoDB 4.4</li>\n  <li>Install NodeJs 15</li>\n  <li>Install Apache</li>\n  <li>Install PHP 7.4</li>\n  <li>Install PM2</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>VFCS Development</h1>\n<h2>Prepare</h2>\n<h3>Buat Direktori API dan Webpanel</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/\nsudo mkdir /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</code></pre>\n<h3>Beri Hak Akses Pada Direktori</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo chmod 777 -R /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/\nsudo chmod 777 -R /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</code></pre>\n<h3>Integrasi Direktori di VPS Dengan Repositori</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/\nsudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin git@github.com:kreasialamteknologi/vfcs_api_realtime.git\ncd /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/\nsudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin git@github.com:kreasialamteknologi/vfcs_webpanel.git</code></p