https://vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id:3000/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Mongo URL</td>\n        <td>mongodb://vfcsmongo:vfcsmongo123@10.74.224.143:27017/db_vfcs?authSource=db_vfcs</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path API (on instance app)</td>\n        <td>/var/www/vfcs_api_live/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path Webpanel (on instance app)</td>\n        <td>/var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path MongoDB backup dump files</td>\n        <td>/var/database_backup_files/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path API uploaded files</td>\n        <td>/var/uploaded_backup_files/</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</figure>\n<h2>Connect</h2>\n<h3>Akses ke AWS</h3>\n<p>VFCS production server hanya bisa diakses di IP 103.152.118.42, sambung ke VPS KAT terlebih dahulu</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh root@103.152.118.42</code></pre>\n<p>Masuk ke direktori dimana credential AWS disimpan. Path direktori berada di /home/VFCS_AWS</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /home/VFCS_AWS/</code></pre>\n<h3>Menyambungkan melalui SSH</h3>\n<p>Terdapat 2 credential yang akan digunakan untuk masuk ke AWS VSI, katdbvfcs.pem dan katappvfcs.pem gunakan salahsatu. Dengan user yang sama dengan nama .pem file, dengan alamat ip 13.228.203.38</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katdbvfcs.pem katdbvfcs@13.228.203.38</code></pre>\n<p>Setelah berhasil, masuk ke salahsatu instance. Jika masuk ke instance DB dengan alamat ip 10.74.224.143</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katdbvfcs.pem katdbvfcs@10.74.224.143</code></pre>\n<p>Jika masuk ke instance App yang berisikan API dan Webpanel dengan alamat ip 10.74.224.89</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katappvfcs.pem katappvfcs@10.74.224.89</code></pre>\n<h2>Prepare</h2>\n<p>Masuk ke instance MongoDB untuk mempersiapkan database terlebih dahulu</p>\n<h3>Buat User MongoDB</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">mongo mongodb://user_admin:pass_admin@ip_address:mongo_port/admin?authSource=admin</code></pre>\n<p>Syntax query create user mongodb</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">db.createUser({user: \"vfcsmongo\", pass: \"vfcsmongo123\", roles: [{role: readWrite, db: db_vfcs}]});</code></pre>\n<h3>Konfigurasi Otomatis Backup Database</h3>\n<p>Buat Folder untuk backup</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/database_backup_files/\nsudo chmod 733 -R /var/database_backup_files/</code></pre>\n<p>Buat bash script backup database</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /etc/backup_db.sh</code></pre>\n<p>File Konfigurasi Backup&nbsp;</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">#!/bin/sh\nDIR=`date +%y%m%d`\nDEST=/home/dbvfcs_backups/$DIR\nmkdir $DEST\nmongodump -h 127.0.0.1 -d db_vfcs -u vfcsmongo -p vfcsmongo123 --authenticationDatabase db_vfcs -o $DEST\nfind /home/dbvfcs_backups/* -mtime +30 -exec rm -R {} \\;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Tambah di Crontab</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">crontab -e</code></pre>\n<p>Tambahkan script di akhir file</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">&nbsp;0 0 */2 * * bash /etc/backup.sh</code></pre>\n<h3>Akses Database mongoDB VFCS</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">mongo mongodb://vfcsmongo:vfcsmongo123@10.74.224.143:27017/db_vfcs?authSource=db_vfcs</code></pre>\n<p>Setelah itu masuk ke instance App untuk mempersiapkan API dan Webpanel</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Buat Direktori API dan Webpanel</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/www/vfcs_api_live/\nsudo mkdir /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</code></pre>\n<h3>Beri Hak Akses Pada Direktori</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo chmod 777 -R /var/www/vfcs_api_live/\nsudo chmod 777 -R /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</code></pre>\n<h3>Integrasi Direktori di VPS Dengan Repositori</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/vfcs_api_live/\nsudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin git@github.com:kreasialamteknologi/vfcs_api_realtime.git\ncd /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/\nsudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin git@github.com:kreasialamteknologi/vfcs_webpanel.git</code></pre>\n<h3>Buat virtualhost apache dan pasang ssl let\'s encrypt</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /etc/apache2/sites-available/vsi-rpet.conf</code></pre>\n<p>File VirtualHost</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;\n	# The ServerName directive sets the request scheme, hostname and port that\n	# the server uses to identify itself. This is used when creating\n	# redirection URLs. In the context of virtual hosts, the ServerName\n	# specifies what hostname must appear in the request\'s Host: header to\n	# match this virtual host. For the default virtual host (this file) this\n	# value is not decisive as it is used as a last resort host regardless.\n	# However, you must set it for any further virtual host explicitly.\n	ServerName vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id\n\n	#ServerAdmin support@kreasialamteknologi.com\n	DocumentRoot /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/\n	# Available loglevels: trace8, ..., trace1, debug, info, notice, warn,\n	# error, crit, alert, emerg.\n	# It is also possible to configure the loglevel for particular\n	# modules, e.g.\n	#LogLevel info ssl:warn\n\n	ErrorLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/error.log\n	CustomLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/access.log combined\n\n	# For most configuration files from conf-available/, which are\n	# enabled or disabled at a global level, it is possible to\n	# include a line for only one particular virtual host. For example the\n	# following line enables the CGI configuration for this host only\n	# after it has been globally disabled with \"a2disconf\".\n	#Include conf-available/serve-cgi-bin.conf\n	&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;\n\n# vim: syntax=apache ts=4 sw=4 sts=4 sr noet</code></pre>\n<p>Pasang SSL Lets Encrypt</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo a2ensite app-vfcs.conf\nsudo systemctl restart apache2\nsudo certbot --apache -d vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id</code></pre>\n<h2>Deploy</h2>\n<p>Pertama masuk ke instance app untuk deploy API dan Webpanel</p>\n<h3>Sinkronisasi Repositori</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  <p>Lebih baik upload ulang dari server development ke repository dengan menggunakan branch live. Untuk mencegah conflict pada code/repository.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/vfcs_api_live/\nsudo git fetch --all\nsudo git merge origin/live</code></pre>\n<h3>Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi Database dan Port Service API</h3>\n<p>Digunakan agar API bisa berkomunikasi dengan database yang sudah dibuat. File konfigurasi terdapat pada <i>app.js</i></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /var/www/vfcs_api_live/app.js</code></pre>\n<p>File Konfigurasi</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">// Mongo Configuration\n\nmongoose.connect(\'mongodb_connection_string\', { useNewUrlParser: true, useUnifiedTopology: true });\nmongoose.set(\'useCreateIndex\', true);\nconst db = mongoose.connection;\ndb.on(\'error\', console.error.bind(console, \'Connection Error:\'));\n\ndb.once(\'open\', () =&gt; {\n  console.log(\'Successfully connected to MongoDB!\');\n});</code></pre>\n<p>Berikut komposisi untuk isian di <i>mongodb conncetion string :</i></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">mongodb://user:pass@ip_database:port/database?authSource=database&amp;retryWrites=true&amp;w=majority</code></pre>\n<p>Lanjut ke konfigurasi port, berada di file sama dengan konfigurasi :</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">const port = your_port; //Isikan service port API nantinya. Contoh: 3000.\nserver.listen(port, () =&gt; {\n  console.log(`Server Mongo is up and running on port number ${port}`);\n});</code></pre>\n<h3>Install Dependency dan Buat Service NodeJS</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo npm install\nsudo pm2 start app.js</code></pre>\n<p>URL akses untuk API : http://<i>ip_address</i> atau <i>domain</i>:<i>port</i>/</p>\n<h3>Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi API Helpers pada Webpanel</h3>\n<p>Digunakan agar webpanel bisa berkomunikasi dengan API</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/application/helpers/api_helper.php</code></pre>\n<p>File Konfigurasi</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\">function url_api()\n{\n	$url_api = \'your_api_string_access\'; //Isikan URL API untuk akses.\n	return $url_api;\n}</code></pre>\n<h2>Backup API Uploaded Files</h2>\n<h3>Buat Folder untuk backup</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/uploaded_backup_files/\nsudo chmod 755 -R /var/uploaded_backup_files/Buat Bash File untuk backup API Upload Folder</code></pre>\n<h3>Konfigurasi Crontab</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">crontab -e</code></pre>\n<p>Tambahkan di akhir file</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">0 0 */2 * * tar -czf /var/backup_uploaded_files/vfcs_api_$(date +%d-%b-%Y).tar.gz /var/www/vfcs_api_live/public/uploads/\n0 0 */5 * * find /var/backup_uploaded_files/vfcs_api_* -mtime +10 -exec rm {} \\; &amp;&gt; /dev/null</code></pre>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Additional</h1>\n<h2>Restore Database Dari Development Server ke Production</h2>\n<p>Sebelum di backup dan deploy ke production, kosongkan data pada collections jika berupa data transaksi. Jika berupa data master dan data yang tersimpan pada collections akan digunakan juga di production, baiknya jangan dikosongkan.</p>\n<h3>Prepare</h3>\n<p>Setelah di backup, copy dump file backup ke AWS VSI. Masuk ke folder dimana credential AWS disimpan.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /home/VFCS_AWS/</code></pre>\n<p>Copy dump file hasil backup ke AWS VSI</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">scp -i /path/to/your/key/.pem -r /copy/from/path user@server:/copy/to/path</code></pre>\n<p>Contoh : Folder backup berada di \"/home/db_vfcs\"</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">scp -i /home/VFCS_AWS/katdbvfcs.pem -r /home/db_vfcs/ katdbvfcs@13.228.203.38:/home/katdbvfcs/</code></pre>\n<h3>Restore</h3>\n<p>Masuk ke AWS VSI</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katdbvfcs.pem katdbvfcs@13.228.203.38</code></pre>\n<p>Copy ke database instance</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">scp -i katdbvfcs.pem -r /home/katdbvfcs/db_vfcs/ katdbvfcs@10.74.224.143:~/</code></pre>\n<p>Masuk ke database instance</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katdbvfcs.pem katdbvfcs@10.74.224.143</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Restore mongoDB</strong></p>\n<p>Jika ingin merestore semua collection hasil backup</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mongorestore mongo_url /path/source/dump/mongoDB/</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mongorestore mongodb://vfcsmongo:vfcsmongo123@127.0.0.1:27017/db_vfcs?authSource=db_vfcs db_vfcs/</code></pre>\n<p>Jika hanya ingin me-<i>restore</i> satu collections atau beberapa collections</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mongorestore mongo_url --collection collection_name path/source/dump.bson\n</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mongorestore mongodb://vfcsmongo:vfcsmongo123@127.0.0.1:27017/db_vfcs?authSource=db_vfcs --collection permissions db_vfcs/permissions.bson</code></pre>\n','html','2021-09-10T14:15:57.523Z','ckeditor','en',3,'2021-09-10T07:14:01.518Z','{}'),(73,'projects/smart-project','e2def6d909de6b56adfb52ddd1f9dabba6d7b958','Smart PLN Project','Describe SMART Project',0,1,'','','updated',10,'<h1>Development</h1>\n<h2>Akses Oracle Database</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<figure class=\"table\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"2\">Spesifikasi Database</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Jenis Database</td>\n        <td>Oracle 11g XE</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>IP</td>\n        <td>103.152.118.94</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Port</td>\n        <td>1520</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Id Container</td>\n        <td>e2ab1ed62101</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Nama Container</td>\n        <td>pedantic_murdock</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>User</td>\n        <td>smartapi_dummy</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>P