"title\":\"File konfigurasi odoo.conf\",\"anchor\":\"#file-konfigurasi-odooconf-7\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"title\":\"3. Mengaktifkan service odoo13-kac\",\"anchor\":\"#h-3-mengaktifkan-service-odoo13-kac\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"4. Odoo bisa diakses dengan port 8113\",\"anchor\":\"#h-4-odoo-bisa-diakses-dengan-port-8113\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"title\":\"D. Konfigurasi NGINX webserver\",\"anchor\":\"#d-konfigurasi-nginx-webserver-3\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"Membuat file virtualhost\",\"anchor\":\"#membuat-file-virtualhost-3\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"File virtualhost app.kreasiacademy.com.conf\",\"anchor\":\"#file-virtualhost-appkreasiacademycomconf\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"title\":\"Enabling virtualhost\",\"anchor\":\"#enabling-virtualhost-3\",\"children\":[]}]}]}]','html','2021-08-25T07:30:57.069Z','2021-09-13T03:07:07.933Z','ckeditor','en',3,1,'{\"js\":\"\",\"css\":\"\"}'),(3,'projects/vfcs','dd02c02c7cd532df91466750b847a89ddbb5d3a4','VFCS Project','Describe how to access and manage',0,1,NULL,'','','<h1>Requirement</h1>\n<ol>\n  <li>Install MongoDB 4.4</li>\n  <li>Install NodeJs 15</li>\n  <li>Install Apache</li>\n  <li>Install PHP 7.4</li>\n  <li>Install PM2</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>VFCS Development</h1>\n<h2>Prepare</h2>\n<h3>Buat Direktori API dan Webpanel</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/\nsudo mkdir /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</code></pre>\n<h3>Beri Hak Akses Pada Direktori</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo chmod 777 -R /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/\nsudo chmod 777 -R /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</code></pre>\n<h3>Integrasi Direktori di VPS Dengan Repositori</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/\nsudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin git@github.com:kreasialamteknologi/vfcs_api_realtime.git\ncd /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/\nsudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin git@github.com:kreasialamteknologi/vfcs_webpanel.git</code></pre>\n<h3>Buat User MongoDB 4.4</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">mongo mongodb://katadmin:katadmin123@103.152.118.94:27017/admin?authSource=admin</code></pre>\n<p>Syntax query create user mongodb</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">db.createUser({user: \"katmongo\", pass: \"katmongo123\", roles: [{role: readWrite, db: db_vfcs}]});</code></pre>\n<h3>Buat virtualhost apache dan pasang ssl let\'s encrypt</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">nano /etc/apache2/sites-available/app-vfcs.conf</code></pre>\n<p>File VirtualHost</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;\n	# The ServerName directive sets the request scheme, hostname and port that\n	# the server uses to identify itself. This is used when creating\n	# redirection URLs. In the context of virtual hosts, the ServerName\n	# specifies what hostname must appear in the request\'s Host: header to\n	# match this virtual host. For the default virtual host (this file) this\n	# value is not decisive as it is used as a last resort host regardless.\n	# However, you must set it for any further virtual host explicitly.\n	ServerName app-vfcs.greenholespace.co.id\n\n	ServerAdmin support@kreasialamteknologi.com\n	DocumentRoot /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/\n	# Available loglevels: trace8, ..., trace1, debug, info, notice, warn,\n	# error, crit, alert, emerg.\n	# It is also possible to configure the loglevel for particular\n	# modules, e.g.\n	#LogLevel info ssl:warn\n\n	ErrorLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/error.log\n	CustomLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/access.log combined\n\n	# For most configuration files from conf-available/, which are\n	# enabled or disabled at a global level, it is possible to\n	# include a line for only one particular virtual host. For example the\n	# following line enables the CGI configuration for this host only\n	# after it has been globally disabled with \"a2disconf\".\n	#Include conf-available/serve-cgi-bin.conf\n	&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;\n\n# vim: syntax=apache ts=4 sw=4 sts=4 sr noet</code></pre>\n<p>Pasang SSL Lets Encrypt</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo a2ensite app-vfcs.conf\nsystemctl restart apache2\nsudo certbot --apache -d app-vfcs.greenholespace.co.id</code></pre>\n<h2>Deploy</h2>\n<h3>Sinkronisasi Repositori</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/\nsudo git pull --all</code></pre>\n<h3>Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi Database dan Port Service API</h3>\n<p>Digunakan agar API bisa berkomunikasi dengan database yang sudah dibuat. File konfigurasi terdapat pada <i>app.js</i></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">nano /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/app.js</code></pre>\n<p>File Konfigurasi</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">// Mongo Configuration\n\nmongoose.connect(\'mongodb_connection_string\', { useNewUrlParser: true, useUnifiedTopology: true });\nmongoose.set(\'useCreateIndex\', true);\nconst db = mongoose.connection;\ndb.on(\'error\', console.error.bind(console, \'Connection Error:\'));\n\ndb.once(\'open\', () =&gt; {\n  console.log(\'Successfully connected to MongoDB!\');\n});</code></pre>\n<p>Berikut komposisi untuk isian di <i>mongodb conncetion string :</i></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">mongodb://user:pass@ip_database:port/database?authSource=database&amp;retryWrites=true&amp;w=majority</code></pre>\n<p>Lanjut ke konfigurasi port, berada di file sama dengan konfigurasi :</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">const port = your_port; //Isikan service port API nantinya. Contoh: 911.\nserver.listen(port, () =&gt; {\n  console.log(`Server Mongo is up and running on port number ${port}`);\n});</code></pre>\n<h3>Install Dependency dan Buat Service NodeJS</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo npm install\nsudo pm2 start app.js</code></pre>\n<p>URL akses untuk API : http://<i>ip_address</i> atau <i>domain</i>:<i>port</i>/</p>\n<h3>Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi API Helpers pada Webpanel</h3>\n<p>Digunakan agar webpanel bisa berkomunikasi dengan API</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">nano /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/application/helpers/api_helper.php</code></pre>\n<p>File Konfigurasi</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\">function url_api()\n{\n	$url_api = \'your_api_string_access\'; //Isikan URL API untuk akses.\n	return $url_api;\n}</code></pre>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>VFCS Live</h1>\n<p>Requirement yang dibutuhkan sama dengan development, pastikan sudah terinstall semua. Untuk domain menggunakan ‚Äò<i>vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id</i>‚Äô</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<figure class=\"table\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"2\">\n          <p style=\"text-align:center;\">VFCS Description</p>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Domain</td>\n        <td>vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>IP Address VPN AWS VSI</td>\n        <td><code>katdbvfcs@13.228.203.38</code></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path .pem file</td>\n        <td>kreasialamteknologi@103.152.118.42:/home/VFCS_AWS/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>IP Address App (API dan Webpanel)</td>\n        <td><code>katappvfcs@10.74.224.89</code></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>IP Address Mongo Database</td>\n        <td><code>katdbvfcs10.74.224.143</code></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Password Sudoers</td>\n        <td>Spring2021</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>API URL</td>\n        <td>https://vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id:3000/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Mongo URL</td>\n        <td>mongodb://vfcsmongo:vfcsmongo123@10.74.224.143:27017/db_vfcs?authSource=db_vfcs</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path API (on instance app)</td>\n        <td>/var/www/vfcs_api_live/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path Webpanel (on instance app)</td>\n        <td>/var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path MongoDB backup dump files</td>\n        <td>/var/database_backup_files/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path API uploaded files</td>\n        <td>/var/uploaded_backup_files/</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</figure>\n<h2>Connect</h2>\n<h3>Akses ke AWS</h3>\n<p>VFCS production server hanya bisa diakses di IP 103.152.118.42, sambung ke VPS KAT terlebih dahulu</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh root@103.152.118.42</code></pre>\n<p>Masuk ke direktori dimana credential AWS disimpan. Path direktori berada di /home/VFCS_AWS</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /home/VFCS_AWS/</code></pre>\n<h3>Menyambungkan melalui SSH</h3>\n<p>Terdapat 2 credential yang akan digunakan untuk masuk ke AWS VSI, katdbvfcs.pem dan katappvfcs.pem gunakan salahsatu. Dengan user yang sama dengan nama .pem file, dengan alamat ip 13.228.203.38</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katdbvfcs.pem katdbvfcs@13.228.203.38</code></pre>\n<p>Setelah berhasil, masuk ke salahsatu instance. Jika masuk ke instance DB dengan alamat ip 10.74.224.143</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katdbvfcs.pem katdbvfcs@10.74.224.143</code></pre>\n<p>Jika masuk ke instance App yang berisikan API dan Webpanel dengan alamat ip 10.74.224.89</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katappvfcs.pem katappvfcs@10.74.224.89</code></pre>\n<h2>Prepare</h2>\n<p>Masuk ke instance MongoDB untuk mempersiapkan database terlebih dahulu</p>\n<h3>Buat User MongoDB</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">mongo mongodb://user_admin:pass_admin@ip_address:mongo_port/admin?authSource=admin</code></pre>\n<p>Syntax query create user mongodb</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">db.createUser({user: \"vfcsmongo\", pass: \"vfcsmongo123\", roles: [{role: readWrite, db: db_vfcs}]});</code></pre>\n<h3>Konfigurasi Otomatis Backup Database</h3>\n<p>Buat Folder untuk backup</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/database_backup_files/\nsudo chmod 733 -R /var/database_backup_files/</code></pre>\n<p>Buat bash script backup database</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /etc/backup_db.sh</code></pre>\n<p>File Konfigurasi Backup&nbsp;</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">#!/bin/sh\nDIR=`date +%y%m%d`\nDEST=/home/dbvfcs_backups/$DIR\nmkdir $DEST\nmongodump -h 127.0.0.1 -d db_vfcs -u vfcsmongo -p vfcsmongo123 --authenticationDatabase db_vfcs -o $DEST\nfind /home/dbvfcs_backups/* -mtime +30 -exec rm -R {} \\;\n</code></pre>\n<p>Tambah di Crontab</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">crontab -e</code></pre>\n<p>Tambahkan script di akhir file</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">&nbsp;0 0 */2 * * bash /etc/backup.sh</code></pre>\n<h3>Akses Database mongoDB VFCS</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">mongo mongodb://vfcsmongo:vfcsmongo123@10.74.224.143:27017/db_vfcs?authSource=db_vfcs</code></pre>\n<p>Setelah itu masuk ke instance App untuk mempersiapkan API dan Webpanel</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Buat Direktori API dan Webpanel</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/www/vfcs_api_live/\nsudo mkdir /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</code></pre>\n<h3>Beri Hak Akses Pada Direktori</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo chmod 777 -R /var/www/vfcs_api_live/\nsudo chmod 777 -R /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</code></pre>\n<h3>Integrasi Direktori di VPS Dengan Repositori</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/vfcs_api_live/\nsudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin git@github.com:kreasialamteknologi/vfcs_api_realtime.git\ncd /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/\nsudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin git@github.com:kreasialamteknologi/vfcs_webpanel.git</code></pre>\n<h3>Buat virtualhost apache dan pasang ssl let\'s encrypt</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /etc/apache2/sites-available/vsi-rpet.conf</code></pre>\n<p>File VirtualHost</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;\n	# The ServerName directive sets the request scheme, hostname and port that\n	# the server uses to identify itself. This is used when creating\n	# redirection URLs. In the context of virtual hosts, the ServerName\n	# specifies what hostname must appear in the request\'s Host: header to\n	# match this virtual host. For the default virtual host (this file) this\n	# value is not decisive as it is used as a last resort host regardless.\n	# However, you must set it for any further virtual host explicitly.\n	ServerName vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id\n\n	#ServerAdmin support@kreasialamteknologi.com\n	DocumentRoot /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/\n	# Available loglevels: trace8, ..., trace1, debug, info, notice, warn,\n	# error, crit, alert, emerg.\n	# It is also possible to configure the loglevel for particular\n	# modules, e.g.\n	#LogLevel info ssl:warn\n\n	ErrorLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/error.log\n	CustomLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/access.log combined\n\n	# For most configuration files from conf-available/, which are\n	# enabled or disabled at a global level, it is possible to\n	# include a line for only one particular virtual host. For example the\n	# following line enables the CGI configuration for this host only\n	# after it has been globally disabled with \"a2disconf\".\n	#Include conf-available/serve-cgi-bin.conf\n	&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;\n\n# vim: syntax=apache ts=4 sw=4 sts=4 sr noet</code></pre>\n<p>Pasang SSL Lets Encrypt</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo a2ensite app-vfcs.conf\nsudo systemctl restart apache2\nsudo certbot --apache -d vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id</code></pre>\n<h2>Deploy</h2>\n<p>Pertama masuk ke instance app untuk deploy API dan Webpanel</p>\n<h3>Sinkronisasi Repositori</h3>\n<blockquote>\n  <p>Lebih baik upload ulang dari server development ke repository dengan menggunakan branch live. Untuk mencegah conflict pada code/repository.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/vfcs_api_live/\nsudo git fetch --all\nsudo git merge origin/live</code></pre>\n<h3>Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi Database dan Port Service API</h3>\n<p>Digunakan agar API bisa berkomunikasi dengan database yang sudah dibuat. File konfigurasi terdapat pada <i>app.js</i></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /var/www/vfcs_api_live/app.js</code></pre>\n<p>File Konfigurasi</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">// Mongo Configuration\n\nmongoose.connect(\'mongodb_connection_string\', { useNewUrlParser: true, useUnifiedTopology: true });\nmongoose.set(\'useCreateIndex\', true);\nconst db = mongoose.connection;\ndb.on(\'error\', console.error.bind(console, \'Connection Error:\'));\n\ndb.once(\'open\', () =&gt; {\n  console.log(\'Successfully connected to MongoDB!\');\n});</code></pre>\n<p>Berikut komposisi untuk isian di <i>mongodb conncetion string :</i></p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">mongodb://user:pass@ip_database:port/database?authSource=database&amp;retryWrites=true&amp;w=majority</code></pre>\n<p>Lanjut ke konfigurasi port, berada di file sama dengan konfigurasi :</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-javascript\">const port = your_port; //Isikan service port API nantinya. Contoh: 3000.\nserver.listen(port, () =&gt; {\n  console.log(`Server Mongo is up and running on port number ${port}`);\n});</code></pre>\n<h3>Install Dependency dan Buat Service NodeJS</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo npm install\nsudo pm2 start app.js</code></pre>\n<p>URL akses untuk API : http://<i>ip_address</i> atau <i>domain</i>:<i>port</i>/</p>\n<h3>Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi API Helpers pada Webpanel</h3>\n<p>Digunakan agar webpanel bisa berkomunikasi dengan API</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/application/helpers/api_helper.php</code></pre>\n<p>File Konfigurasi</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\">function url_api()\n{\n	$url_api = \'your_api_string_access\'; //Isikan URL API untuk akses.\n	return $url_api;\n}</code></pre>\n<h2>Backup API Uploaded Files</h2>\n<h3>Buat Folder untuk backup</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/uploaded_backup_files/\nsudo chmod 755 -R /var/uploaded_backup_files/Buat Bash File untuk backup API Upload Folder</code></pre>\n<h3>Konfigurasi Crontab</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">crontab -e</code></pre>\n<p>Tambahkan di akhir file</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">0 0 */2 * * tar -czf /var/backup_uploaded_files/vfcs_api_$(date +%d-%b-%Y).tar.gz /var/www/vfcs_api_live/public/uploads/\n0 0 */5 * * find /var/backup_uploaded_files/vfcs_api_* -mtime +10 -exec rm {} \\; &amp;&gt; /dev/null</code></pre>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Additional</h1>\n<h2>Restore Database Dari Development Server ke Production</h2>\n<p>Sebelum di backup dan deploy ke production, kosongkan data pada collections jika berupa data transaksi. Jika berupa data master dan data yang tersimpan pada collections akan digunakan juga di production, baiknya jangan dikosongkan.</p>\n<h3>Prepare</h3>\n<p>Setelah di backup, copy dump file backup ke AWS VSI. Masuk ke folder dimana credential AWS disimpan.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /home/VFCS_AWS/</code></pre>\n<p>Copy dump file hasil backup ke AWS VSI</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">scp -i /path/to/your/key/.pem -r /copy/from/path user@server:/copy/to/path</code></pre>\n<p>Contoh : Folder backup berada di \"/home/db_vfcs\"</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">scp -i /home/VFCS_AWS/katdbvfcs.pem -r /home/db_vfcs/ katdbvfcs@13.228.203.38:/home/katdbvfcs/</code></pre>\n<h3>Restore</h3>\n<p>Masuk ke AWS VSI</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katdbvfcs.pem katdbvfcs@13.228.203.38</code></pre>\n<p>Copy ke database instance</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">scp -i katdbvfcs.pem -r /home/katdbvfcs/db_vfcs/ katdbvfcs@10.74.224.143:~/</code></pre>\n<p>Masuk ke database instance</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katdbvfcs.pem katdbvfcs@10.74.224.143</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Restore mongoDB</strong></p>\n<p>Jika ingin merestore semua collection hasil backup</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mongorestore mongo_url /path/source/dump/mongoDB/</code></pre>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mongorestore mongodb://vfcsmongo:vfcsmongo123@127.0.0.1:27017/db_vfcs?authSource=db_vfcs db_vfcs/</code></pre>\n<p>Jika hanya ingin me-<i>restore</i> satu collections atau beberapa collections</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mongorestore mongo_url --collection collection_name path/source/dump.bson\n</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mongorestore mongodb://vfcsmongo:vfcsmongo123@127.0.0.1:27017/db_vfcs?authSource=db_vfcs --collection permissions db_vfcs/permissions.bson</code></pre>\n<h2>Restart API</h2>\n<p>Restart API dibutuhkan ketika web atau mobile tidak bisa melakukan transaksi, seperti login, dashboard, atau input data baru. Di project VFCS API menggunakan NodeJS untuk deployment di server menggunakan pm2. Masuk dulu ke instance app VFCS untuk me-<i>restart </i>API.</p>\n<p>Pertama, cek nama service di pm2</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo pm2 status</code></pre>\n<p>List nama service akan muncul</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Jika tidak ada atau kosong, ada indikasi bahwa service mati. Masuk ke direktori API, dan start service menggunakan pm2</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo pm2 start app.js</code></pre>\n<p>Kedua, jika nama service masih ada. Restart service nodejs</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo pm2 restart nama_service</code></pre>\n<p>Untuk cek apakah berjalan normal, masuk ke log service aplikasi tersebut</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo pm2 log nama_service</code></pre>\n<p>Jika terdapat error koneksi database, ada kemungkinan database mati/<i>bottleneck. </i>Restart database.</p>\n<h2>Restart Mongo Database</h2>\n<p>Ketika log API terdapat error koneksi database, baiknya database di cek atau direstart. Terdapat perbedaan dalam penggunaan environment di dev dan production untuk database. Pada development menggunakan container docker, sedangkan pada production terinstal di dalam instance. Hal pertama yang dilakukan adalah login ke instance DB VFCS.</p>\n<p>Selanjutnya, cek koneksi database melalui mongo CLI</p>\n<p>Pada development,</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Pada Production,&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','<h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"requirement\"><a href=\"#requirement\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Requirement</h1><div>\n</div><ol>\n  <li>Install MongoDB 4.4</li>\n  <li>Install NodeJs 15</li>\n  <li>Install Apache</li>\n  <li>Install PHP 7.4</li>\n  <li>Install PM2</li>\n</ol><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"vfcs-development\"><a href=\"#vfcs-development\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> VFCS Development</h1><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"prepare\"><a href=\"#prepare\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Prepare</h2><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"buat-direktori-api-dan-webpanel\"><a href=\"#buat-direktori-api-dan-webpanel\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Buat Direktori API dan Webpanel</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/\nsudo mkdir /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"beri-hak-akses-pada-direktori\"><a href=\"#beri-hak-akses-pada-direktori\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Beri Hak Akses Pada Direktori</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo chmod 777 -R /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/\nsudo chmod 777 -R /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"integrasi-direktori-di-vps-dengan-repositori\"><a href=\"#integrasi-direktori-di-vps-dengan-repositori\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Integrasi Direktori di VPS Dengan Repositori</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/\nsudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin git@github.com:kreasialamteknologi/vfcs_api_realtime.git\ncd /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/\nsudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin git@github.com:kreasialamteknologi/vfcs_webpanel.git</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"buat-user-mongodb-44\"><a href=\"#buat-user-mongodb-44\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Buat User MongoDB 4.4</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">mongo mongodb://katadmin:katadmin123@103.152.118.94:27017/admin?authSource=admin</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Syntax query create user mongodb</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">db.createUser({user: \"katmongo\", pass: \"katmongo123\", roles: [{role: readWrite, db: db_vfcs}]});</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"buat-virtualhost-apache-dan-pasang-ssl-lets-encrypt\"><a href=\"#buat-virtualhost-apache-dan-pasang-ssl-lets-encrypt\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Buat virtualhost apache dan pasang ssl let\'s encrypt</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">nano /etc/apache2/sites-available/app-vfcs.conf</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>File VirtualHost</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;\n	# The ServerName directive sets the request scheme, hostname and port that\n	# the server uses to identify itself. This is used when creating\n	# redirection URLs. In the context of virtual hosts, the ServerName\n	# specifies what hostname must appear in the request\'s Host: header to\n	# match this virtual host. For the default virtual host (this file) this\n	# value is not decisive as it is used as a last resort host regardless.\n	# However, you must set it for any further virtual host explicitly.\n	ServerName app-vfcs.greenholespace.co.id\n\n	ServerAdmin support@kreasialamteknologi.com\n	DocumentRoot /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/\n	# Available loglevels: trace8, ..., trace1, debug, info, notice, warn,\n	# error, crit, alert, emerg.\n	# It is also possible to configure the loglevel for particular\n	# modules, e.g.\n	#LogLevel info ssl:warn\n\n	ErrorLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/error.log\n	CustomLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/access.log combined\n\n	# For most configuration files from conf-available/, which are\n	# enabled or disabled at a global level, it is possible to\n	# include a line for only one particular virtual host. For example the\n	# following line enables the CGI configuration for this host only\n	# after it has been globally disabled with \"a2disconf\".\n	#Include conf-available/serve-cgi-bin.conf\n	&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;\n\n# vim: syntax=apache ts=4 sw=4 sts=4 sr noet</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Pasang SSL Lets Encrypt</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo a2ensite app-vfcs.conf\nsystemctl restart apache2\nsudo certbot --apache -d app-vfcs.greenholespace.co.id</code></pre><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"deploy\"><a href=\"#deploy\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Deploy</h2><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"sinkronisasi-repositori\"><a href=\"#sinkronisasi-repositori\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Sinkronisasi Repositori</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/\nsudo git pull --all</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"sinkronisasi-konfigurasi-database-dan-port-service-api\"><a href=\"#sinkronisasi-konfigurasi-database-dan-port-service-api\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi Database dan Port Service API</h3><div>\n</div><p>Digunakan agar API bisa berkomunikasi dengan database yang sudah dibuat. File konfigurasi terdapat pada <i>app.js</i></p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">nano /var/www/vfcs_api_dummy/app.js</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>File Konfigurasi</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">// Mongo Configuration\n\nmongoose.connect(\'mongodb_connection_string\', { useNewUrlParser: true, useUnifiedTopology: true });\nmongoose.set(\'useCreateIndex\', true);\nconst db = mongoose.connection;\ndb.on(\'error\', console.error.bind(console, \'Connection Error:\'));\n\ndb.once(\'open\', () =&gt; {\n  console.log(\'Successfully connected to MongoDB!\');\n});</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Berikut komposisi untuk isian di <i>mongodb conncetion string :</i></p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">mongodb://user:pass@ip_database:port/database?authSource=database&amp;retryWrites=true&amp;w=majority</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Lanjut ke konfigurasi port, berada di file sama dengan konfigurasi :</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">const port = your_port; //Isikan service port API nantinya. Contoh: 911.\nserver.listen(port, () =&gt; {\n  console.log(`Server Mongo is up and running on port number ${port}`);\n});</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"install-dependency-dan-buat-service-nodejs\"><a href=\"#install-dependency-dan-buat-service-nodejs\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Install Dependency dan Buat Service NodeJS</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo npm install\nsudo pm2 start app.js</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>URL akses untuk API : http://<i>ip_address</i> atau <i>domain</i>:<i>port</i>/</p><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"sinkronisasi-konfigurasi-api-helpers-pada-webpanel\"><a href=\"#sinkronisasi-konfigurasi-api-helpers-pada-webpanel\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi API Helpers pada Webpanel</h3><div>\n</div><p>Digunakan agar webpanel bisa berkomunikasi dengan API</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">nano /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/application/helpers/api_helper.php</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>File Konfigurasi</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-php\">function url_api()\n{\n	$url_api = \'your_api_string_access\'; //Isikan URL API untuk akses.\n	return $url_api;\n}</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"vfcs-live\"><a href=\"#vfcs-live\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> VFCS Live</h1><div>\n</div><p>Requirement yang dibutuhkan sama dengan development, pastikan sudah terinstall semua. Untuk domain menggunakan ‚Äò<i>vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id</i>‚Äô</p><div>\n</div><p>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div><figure class=\"table\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"2\">\n          <p style=\"text-align:center;\">VFCS Description</p>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Domain</td>\n        <td>vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>IP Address VPN AWS VSI</td>\n        <td><code>katdbvfcs@13.228.203.38</code></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path .pem file</td>\n        <td>kreasialamteknologi@103.152.118.42:/home/VFCS_AWS/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>IP Address App (API dan Webpanel)</td>\n        <td><code>katappvfcs@10.74.224.89</code></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>IP Address Mongo Database</td>\n        <td><code>katdbvfcs10.74.224.143</code></td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Password Sudoers</td>\n        <td>Spring2021</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>API URL</td>\n        <td>https://vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id:3000/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Mongo URL</td>\n        <td>mongodb://vfcsmongo:vfcsmongo123@10.74.224.143:27017/db_vfcs?authSource=db_vfcs</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path API (on instance app)</td>\n        <td>/var/www/vfcs_api_live/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path Webpanel (on instance app)</td>\n        <td>/var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path MongoDB backup dump files</td>\n        <td>/var/database_backup_files/</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Folder path API uploaded files</td>\n        <td>/var/uploaded_backup_files/</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</figure><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"connect\"><a href=\"#connect\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Connect</h2><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"akses-ke-aws\"><a href=\"#akses-ke-aws\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Akses ke AWS</h3><div>\n</div><p>VFCS production server hanya bisa diakses di IP 103.152.118.42, sambung ke VPS KAT terlebih dahulu</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh root@103.152.118.42</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Masuk ke direktori dimana credential AWS disimpan. Path direktori berada di /home/VFCS_AWS</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /home/VFCS_AWS/</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"menyambungkan-melalui-ssh\"><a href=\"#menyambungkan-melalui-ssh\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Menyambungkan melalui SSH</h3><div>\n</div><p>Terdapat 2 credential yang akan digunakan untuk masuk ke AWS VSI, katdbvfcs.pem dan katappvfcs.pem gunakan salahsatu. Dengan user yang sama dengan nama .pem file, dengan alamat ip 13.228.203.38</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katdbvfcs.pem katdbvfcs@13.228.203.38</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Setelah berhasil, masuk ke salahsatu instance. Jika masuk ke instance DB dengan alamat ip 10.74.224.143</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katdbvfcs.pem katdbvfcs@10.74.224.143</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Jika masuk ke instance App yang berisikan API dan Webpanel dengan alamat ip 10.74.224.89</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katappvfcs.pem katappvfcs@10.74.224.89</code></pre><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"prepare-1\"><a href=\"#prepare-1\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Prepare</h2><div>\n</div><p>Masuk ke instance MongoDB untuk mempersiapkan database terlebih dahulu</p><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"buat-user-mongodb\"><a href=\"#buat-user-mongodb\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Buat User MongoDB</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">mongo mongodb://user_admin:pass_admin@ip_address:mongo_port/admin?authSource=admin</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Syntax query create user mongodb</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">db.createUser({user: \"vfcsmongo\", pass: \"vfcsmongo123\", roles: [{role: readWrite, db: db_vfcs}]});</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"konfigurasi-otomatis-backup-database\"><a href=\"#konfigurasi-otomatis-backup-database\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Konfigurasi Otomatis Backup Database</h3><div>\n</div><p>Buat Folder untuk backup</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/database_backup_files/\nsudo chmod 733 -R /var/database_backup_files/</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Buat bash script backup database</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /etc/backup_db.sh</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>File Konfigurasi Backup&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">#!/bin/sh\nDIR=`date +%y%m%d`\nDEST=/home/dbvfcs_backups/$DIR\nmkdir $DEST\nmongodump -h 127.0.0.1 -d db_vfcs -u vfcsmongo -p vfcsmongo123 --authenticationDatabase db_vfcs -o $DEST\nfind /home/dbvfcs_backups/* -mtime +30 -exec rm -R {} \\;\n</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Tambah di Crontab</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">crontab -e</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Tambahkan script di akhir file</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">&nbsp;0 0 */2 * * bash /etc/backup.sh</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"akses-database-mongodb-vfcs\"><a href=\"#akses-database-mongodb-vfcs\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Akses Database mongoDB VFCS</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">mongo mongodb://vfcsmongo:vfcsmongo123@10.74.224.143:27017/db_vfcs?authSource=db_vfcs</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Setelah itu masuk ke instance App untuk mempersiapkan API dan Webpanel</p><div>\n</div><p>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"buat-direktori-api-dan-webpanel-1\"><a href=\"#buat-direktori-api-dan-webpanel-1\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Buat Direktori API dan Webpanel</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/www/vfcs_api_live/\nsudo mkdir /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"beri-hak-akses-pada-direktori-1\"><a href=\"#beri-hak-akses-pada-direktori-1\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Beri Hak Akses Pada Direktori</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo chmod 777 -R /var/www/vfcs_api_live/\nsudo chmod 777 -R /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"integrasi-direktori-di-vps-dengan-repositori-1\"><a href=\"#integrasi-direktori-di-vps-dengan-repositori-1\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Integrasi Direktori di VPS Dengan Repositori</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/vfcs_api_live/\nsudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin git@github.com:kreasialamteknologi/vfcs_api_realtime.git\ncd /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/\nsudo git init\nsudo git remote add origin git@github.com:kreasialamteknologi/vfcs_webpanel.git</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"buat-virtualhost-apache-dan-pasang-ssl-lets-encrypt-1\"><a href=\"#buat-virtualhost-apache-dan-pasang-ssl-lets-encrypt-1\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Buat virtualhost apache dan pasang ssl let\'s encrypt</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /etc/apache2/sites-available/vsi-rpet.conf</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>File VirtualHost</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;\n	# The ServerName directive sets the request scheme, hostname and port that\n	# the server uses to identify itself. This is used when creating\n	# redirection URLs. In the context of virtual hosts, the ServerName\n	# specifies what hostname must appear in the request\'s Host: header to\n	# match this virtual host. For the default virtual host (this file) this\n	# value is not decisive as it is used as a last resort host regardless.\n	# However, you must set it for any further virtual host explicitly.\n	ServerName vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id\n\n	#ServerAdmin support@kreasialamteknologi.com\n	DocumentRoot /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/\n	# Available loglevels: trace8, ..., trace1, debug, info, notice, warn,\n	# error, crit, alert, emerg.\n	# It is also possible to configure the loglevel for particular\n	# modules, e.g.\n	#LogLevel info ssl:warn\n\n	ErrorLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/error.log\n	CustomLog ${APACHE_LOG_DIR}/access.log combined\n\n	# For most configuration files from conf-available/, which are\n	# enabled or disabled at a global level, it is possible to\n	# include a line for only one particular virtual host. For example the\n	# following line enables the CGI configuration for this host only\n	# after it has been globally disabled with \"a2disconf\".\n	#Include conf-available/serve-cgi-bin.conf\n	&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;\n\n# vim: syntax=apache ts=4 sw=4 sts=4 sr noet</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Pasang SSL Lets Encrypt</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo a2ensite app-vfcs.conf\nsudo systemctl restart apache2\nsudo certbot --apache -d vfcs.vsi-rpet.co.id</code></pre><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"deploy-1\"><a href=\"#deploy-1\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Deploy</h2><div>\n</div><p>Pertama masuk ke instance app untuk deploy API dan Webpanel</p><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"sinkronisasi-repositori-1\"><a href=\"#sinkronisasi-repositori-1\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Sinkronisasi Repositori</h3><div>\n</div><blockquote>\n  <p>Lebih baik upload ulang dari server development ke repository dengan menggunakan branch live. Untuk mencegah conflict pada code/repository.</p>\n</blockquote><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /var/www/vfcs_api_live/\nsudo git fetch --all\nsudo git merge origin/live</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"sinkronisasi-konfigurasi-database-dan-port-service-api-1\"><a href=\"#sinkronisasi-konfigurasi-database-dan-port-service-api-1\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi Database dan Port Service API</h3><div>\n</div><p>Digunakan agar API bisa berkomunikasi dengan database yang sudah dibuat. File konfigurasi terdapat pada <i>app.js</i></p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /var/www/vfcs_api_live/app.js</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>File Konfigurasi</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">// Mongo Configuration\n\nmongoose.connect(\'mongodb_connection_string\', { useNewUrlParser: true, useUnifiedTopology: true });\nmongoose.set(\'useCreateIndex\', true);\nconst db = mongoose.connection;\ndb.on(\'error\', console.error.bind(console, \'Connection Error:\'));\n\ndb.once(\'open\', () =&gt; {\n  console.log(\'Successfully connected to MongoDB!\');\n});</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Berikut komposisi untuk isian di <i>mongodb conncetion string :</i></p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">mongodb://user:pass@ip_database:port/database?authSource=database&amp;retryWrites=true&amp;w=majority</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Lanjut ke konfigurasi port, berada di file sama dengan konfigurasi :</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">const port = your_port; //Isikan service port API nantinya. Contoh: 3000.\nserver.listen(port, () =&gt; {\n  console.log(`Server Mongo is up and running on port number ${port}`);\n});</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"install-dependency-dan-buat-service-nodejs-1\"><a href=\"#install-dependency-dan-buat-service-nodejs-1\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Install Dependency dan Buat Service NodeJS</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo npm install\nsudo pm2 start app.js</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>URL akses untuk API : http://<i>ip_address</i> atau <i>domain</i>:<i>port</i>/</p><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"sinkronisasi-konfigurasi-api-helpers-pada-webpanel-1\"><a href=\"#sinkronisasi-konfigurasi-api-helpers-pada-webpanel-1\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi API Helpers pada Webpanel</h3><div>\n</div><p>Digunakan agar webpanel bisa berkomunikasi dengan API</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /var/www/html/vfcs_webpanel/application/helpers/api_helper.php</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>File Konfigurasi</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-php\">function url_api()\n{\n	$url_api = \'your_api_string_access\'; //Isikan URL API untuk akses.\n	return $url_api;\n}</code></pre><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"backup-api-uploaded-files\"><a href=\"#backup-api-uploaded-files\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Backup API Uploaded Files</h2><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"buat-folder-untuk-backup\"><a href=\"#buat-folder-untuk-backup\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Buat Folder untuk backup</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mkdir /var/uploaded_backup_files/\nsudo chmod 755 -R /var/uploaded_backup_files/Buat Bash File untuk backup API Upload Folder</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"konfigurasi-crontab\"><a href=\"#konfigurasi-crontab\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Konfigurasi Crontab</h3><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">crontab -e</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Tambahkan di akhir file</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">0 0 */2 * * tar -czf /var/backup_uploaded_files/vfcs_api_$(date +%d-%b-%Y).tar.gz /var/www/vfcs_api_live/public/uploads/\n0 0 */5 * * find /var/backup_uploaded_files/vfcs_api_* -mtime +10 -exec rm {} \\; &amp;&gt; /dev/null</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"additional\"><a href=\"#additional\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Additional</h1><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"restore-database-dari-development-server-ke-production\"><a href=\"#restore-database-dari-development-server-ke-production\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Restore Database Dari Development Server ke Production</h2><div>\n</div><p>Sebelum di backup dan deploy ke production, kosongkan data pada collections jika berupa data transaksi. Jika berupa data master dan data yang tersimpan pada collections akan digunakan juga di production, baiknya jangan dikosongkan.</p><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"prepare-2\"><a href=\"#prepare-2\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Prepare</h3><div>\n</div><p>Setelah di backup, copy dump file backup ke AWS VSI. Masuk ke folder dimana credential AWS disimpan.</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /home/VFCS_AWS/</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Copy dump file hasil backup ke AWS VSI</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">scp -i /path/to/your/key/.pem -r /copy/from/path user@server:/copy/to/path</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Contoh : Folder backup berada di \"/home/db_vfcs\"</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">scp -i /home/VFCS_AWS/katdbvfcs.pem -r /home/db_vfcs/ katdbvfcs@13.228.203.38:/home/katdbvfcs/</code></pre><div>\n</div><h3 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"restore\"><a href=\"#restore\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Restore</h3><div>\n</div><p>Masuk ke AWS VSI</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katdbvfcs.pem katdbvfcs@13.228.203.38</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Copy ke database instance</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">scp -i katdbvfcs.pem -r /home/katdbvfcs/db_vfcs/ katdbvfcs@10.74.224.143:~/</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Masuk ke database instance</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">ssh -i katdbvfcs.pem katdbvfcs@10.74.224.143</code></pre><div>\n</div><p><strong>Restore mongoDB</strong></p><div>\n</div><p>Jika ingin merestore semua collection hasil backup</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mongorestore mongo_url /path/source/dump/mongoDB/</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mongorestore mongodb://vfcsmongo:vfcsmongo123@127.0.0.1:27017/db_vfcs?authSource=db_vfcs db_vfcs/</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Jika hanya ingin me-<i>restore</i> satu collections atau beberapa collections</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mongorestore mongo_url --collection collection_name path/source/dump.bson\n</code></pre><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo mongorestore mongodb://vfcsmongo:vfcsmongo123@127.0.0.1:27017/db_vfcs?authSource=db_vfcs --collection permissions db_vfcs/permissions.bson</code></pre><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"restart-api\"><a href=\"#restart-api\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Restart API</h2><div>\n</div><p>Restart API dibutuhkan ketika web atau mobile tidak bisa melakukan transaksi, seperti login, dashboard, atau input data baru. Di project VFCS API menggunakan NodeJS untuk deployment di server menggunakan pm2. Masuk dulu ke instance app VFCS untuk me-<i>restart </i>API.</p><div>\n</div><p>Pertama, cek nama service di pm2</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo pm2 status</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>List nama service akan muncul</p><div>\n</div><p>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div><p>Jika tidak ada atau kosong, ada indikasi bahwa service mati. Masuk ke direktori API, dan start service menggunakan pm2</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo pm2 start app.js</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Kedua, jika nama service masih ada. Restart service nodejs</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo pm2 restart nama_service</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Untuk cek apakah berjalan normal, masuk ke log service aplikasi tersebut</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo pm2 log nama_service</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Jika terdapat error koneksi database, ada kemungkinan database mati/<i>bottleneck. </i>Restart database.</p><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"restart-mongo-database\"><a href=\"#restart-mongo-database\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Restart Mongo Database</h2><div>\n</div><p>Ketika log API terdapat error koneksi database, baiknya database di cek atau direstart. Terdapat perbedaan dalam penggunaan environment di dev dan production untuk database. Pada development menggunakan container docker, sedangkan pada production terinstal di dalam instance. Hal pertama yang dilakukan adalah login ke instance DB VFCS.</p><div>\n</div><p>Selanjutnya, cek koneksi database melalui mongo CLI</p><div>\n</div><p>Pada development,</p><div>\n</div><p>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div><p>Pada Production,&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div><p>&nbsp;</p><div>\n</div>','[{\"title\":\"Requirement\",\"anchor\":\"#requirement\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"VFCS Development\",\"anchor\":\"#vfcs-development\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"Prepare\",\"anchor\":\"#prepare\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"Buat Direktori API dan Webpanel\",\"anchor\":\"#buat-direktori-api-dan-webpanel\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Beri Hak Akses Pada Direktori\",\"anchor\":\"#beri-hak-akses-pada-direktori\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Integrasi Direktori di VPS Dengan Repositori\",\"anchor\":\"#integrasi-direktori-di-vps-dengan-repositori\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Buat User MongoDB 4.4\",\"anchor\":\"#buat-user-mongodb-44\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Buat virtualhost apache dan pasang ssl let\'s encrypt\",\"anchor\":\"#buat-virtualhost-apache-dan-pasang-ssl-lets-encrypt\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"title\":\"Deploy\",\"anchor\":\"#deploy\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"Sinkronisasi Repositori\",\"anchor\":\"#sinkronisasi-repositori\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi Database dan Port Service API\",\"anchor\":\"#sinkronisasi-konfigurasi-database-dan-port-service-api\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Install Dependency dan Buat Service NodeJS\",\"anchor\":\"#install-dependency-dan-buat-service-nodejs\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi API Helpers pada Webpanel\",\"anchor\":\"#sinkronisasi-konfigurasi-api-helpers-pada-webpanel\",\"children\":[]}]}]},{\"title\":\"VFCS Live\",\"anchor\":\"#vfcs-live\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"Connect\",\"anchor\":\"#connect\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"Akses ke AWS\",\"anchor\":\"#akses-ke-aws\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Menyambungkan melalui SSH\",\"anchor\":\"#menyambungkan-melalui-ssh\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"title\":\"Prepare\",\"anchor\":\"#prepare-1\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"Buat User MongoDB\",\"anchor\":\"#buat-user-mongodb\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Konfigurasi Otomatis Backup Database\",\"anchor\":\"#konfigurasi-otomatis-backup-database\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Akses Database mongoDB VFCS\",\"anchor\":\"#akses-database-mongodb-vfcs\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Buat Direktori API dan Webpanel\",\"anchor\":\"#buat-direktori-api-dan-webpanel-1\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Beri Hak Akses Pada Direktori\",\"anchor\":\"#beri-hak-akses-pada-direktori-1\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Integrasi Direktori di VPS Dengan Repositori\",\"anchor\":\"#integrasi-direktori-di-vps-dengan-repositori-1\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Buat virtualhost apache dan pasang ssl let\'s encrypt\",\"anchor\":\"#buat-virtualhost-apache-dan-pasang-ssl-lets-encrypt-1\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"title\":\"Deploy\",\"anchor\":\"#deploy-1\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"Sinkronisasi Repositori\",\"anchor\":\"#sinkronisasi-repositori-1\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi Database dan Port Service API\",\"anchor\":\"#sinkronisasi-konfigurasi-database-dan-port-service-api-1\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Install Dependency dan Buat Service NodeJS\",\"anchor\":\"#install-dependency-dan-buat-service-nodejs-1\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Sinkronisasi Konfigurasi API Helpers pada Webpanel\",\"anchor\":\"#sinkronisasi-konfigurasi-api-helpers-pada-webpanel-1\",\"children\":[]}]},{\"title\":\"Backup API Uploaded Files\",\"anchor\":\"#backup-api-uploaded-files\",\"children\":[{\"title\":\"Buat Folder untuk backup\",\"anchor\":\"#buat-folder-untuk-backup\",\"children\":[]},{\"title\":\"Konfigurasi Crontab\",\"anchor\":\"#konfigurasi-crontab\",\"children\":[]}]}]},{\"title\":\"Additional\",\"anchor\":\"#additional\",\"children\":[{