ri repositori</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo git fetch --all\nsudo git merge origin/v2.0</code></pre>\n<h2>Konfigurasi Database</h2>\n<figure class=\"table\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td colspan=\"2\">\n          <p style=\"text-align:center;\">Akses Database Ibiznis App</p>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Jenis Database</td>\n        <td>MySQL 5.6</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Host</td>\n        <td>103.160.62.175</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Port</td>\n        <td>3306</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>ID Container</td>\n        <td>c59c00a257fb&nbsp;</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Nama Container</td>\n        <td>db_ibiznis</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>User Database</td>\n        <td>root</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Password Database</td>\n        <td>Kreasi123*</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</figure>\n<h3>Create Database</h3>\n<p>Akses VPS database terlebih dahulu, kemudian masuk ke MySQL</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">mysql -h 127.0.0.1 -uroot -pKreasi123*</code></pre>\n<p>Buat database</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">create database ibiznis_app;</code></pre>\n<h3>Restore SQL Dump</h3>\n<p>Masih tersambung di CLI MySQL, masuk ke database yang baru dibuat</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">use ibizinis_app;</code></pre>\n<p>Restore SQL Dump yang ada di repositori</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">source /path/to/sqldump/file.sql</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">source /var/www/html/ibiznis_web/db/ibiznis_banyubiru[28032021].sql</code></pre>\n<h3>Edit Konfigurasi Database pada Ibiznis App</h3>\n<p>Buka file konfigurasi database ibiznis app</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /var/www/html/ibiznis_web/application/config/database.php</code></pre>\n<p>File Konfigurasi Database, Tambahkan script berikut :</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">$db[\'default\'][\'hostname\'] = \'127.0.0.1\';\n$db[\'default\'][\'username\'] = \'root\';\n$db[\'default\'][\'password\'] = \'Kreasi123*\';\n$db[\'default\'][\'database\'] = \'ibiznis_app\';</code></pre>\n<h2>Konfigurasi Webserver dan App</h2>\n<h3>Konfigurasi NGINX Webserver</h3>\n<p>Buat file virtualhost di direktori NGINX</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/demo.ibiznis.conf</code></pre>\n<p>Konfigurasi File Virtualhost</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">server {\n	listen 80;\n	listen [::]:80;\n\n	server_name demo.ibiznis.id;\n\n	root /var/www/html/ibiznis_web;\n	# Add index.php to the list if you are using PHP\n    index index.php index.html;\n\n	location / {\n		try_files $uri $uri/ /index.php?$args;\n	}\n}</code></pre>\n<p>Simpan dan buat symlink file di <strong>/etc/nginx/sites-enabled/ </strong>dari file virtualhost</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/demo.ibiznis.conf	/etc/nginx/sites-enabled/</code></pre>\n<p>Restart NGINX</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo systemctl restart nginx</code></pre>\n<h3>Konfigurasi SSL Let\'s Encrypt</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo certbot --nginx -d demo.ibiznis.id</code></pre>\n<p>Tunggu hingga selesai. Jika terdapat pesan <strong>redirect</strong>, pilih <strong>2</strong> atau pilihan <strong>redirect</strong>. Berguna untuk membuat konfigurasi otomatis di virtualhost untuk redirect ke HTTPS ketika membuka website melalui browser dengan protokol HTTP.</p>\n<h3>Konfigurasi Base URL di Ibiznis App</h3>\n<p>Buka file konfigurasi</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /var/www/html/ibiznis_web/application/config/config.php</code></pre>\n<p>Pada konfigurasi base_url, ubah menjadi</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-xml\">/*\n|--------------------------------------------------------------------------\n| Base Site URL\n|--------------------------------------------------------------------------\n|\n| URL to your CodeIgniter root. Typically this will be your base URL,\n| WITH a trailing slash:\n|\n|	http://example.com/\n|\n| WARNING: You MUST set this value!\n|\n| If it is not set, then CodeIgniter will try guess the protocol and path\n| your installation, but due to security concerns the hostname will be set\n| to $_SERVER[\'SERVER_ADDR\'] if available, or localhost otherwise.\n| The auto-detection mechanism exists only for convenience during\n| development and MUST NOT be used in production!\n|\n| If you need to allow multiple domains, remember that this file is still\n| a PHP script and you can easily do that on your own.\n|\n*/\n$config[\'base_url\']	= \'https://demo.ibiznis.id/\';</code></pre>\n','<h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"ibiznis-app\"><a href=\"#ibiznis-app\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Ibiznis App</h1><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"requirement\"><a href=\"#requirement\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Requirement</h2><div>\n</div><ol>\n  <li>PHP</li>\n  <li>Mysql 5.6</li>\n  <li>NGINX Webserver</li>\n  <li>Certbot SSL Let\'s Encrypt</li>\n  <li>GIT</li>\n</ol><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"akses-ibiznis\"><a href=\"#akses-ibiznis\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Akses Ibiznis</h1><div>\n</div><figure class=\"table\">\n  <table>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Domain</td>\n        <td>https://demo.ibiznis.id</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Host</td>\n        <td>103.160.62.175</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>User</td>\n        <td>kreasialamteknologi</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Password</td>\n        <td>Kreasi123*</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Ibiznis App Folder Path</td>\n        <td>/var/www/html/ibiznis_web</td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>Ibiznis App Virtualhost Path</td>\n        <td>/etc/nginx/sites-available/demo.ibiznis.conf</td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</figure><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"install-ibiznis\"><a href=\"#install-ibiznis\" class=\"toc-ancho