\"><a href=\"#backup-wordpress\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Backup Wordpress</h1><div>\n</div><p>Buat bash script untuk backup</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">sudo nano /etc/backup_website.sh</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Bash script backup</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">#Backup KAT Website\n#Backup DB \nmysqldump -h 103.152.118.42 -uroot -pKreasi123* kreasialamteknologi_web &gt; /var/www/html/kreasialamteknologi_web/db/kat_web_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql\n#Delete file\nfind /var/www/html/kreasialamteknologi_web/db/*.sql -mtime +2 -exec rm {} \\;\n#To directory\ncd /var/www/html/kreasialamteknologi_web/\n#Add, Commit and Push file\ngit add .\ngit commit -m \"kat_web_$(date +%Y%m%d).sql\"\ngit push --set-upstream origin master\n#Show completed\necho \"Completed\"</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Simpan dan lanjut ke konfigurasi crontab</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">crontab -e</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Tambah di akhir file</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">0 3 * * * bash /etc/backup_web.sh</code></pre><div>\n</div><h1 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"additional\"><a href=\"#additional\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Additional</h1><div>\n</div><h2 class=\"toc-header\" id=\"cek-konfigurasi-database-wordpress\"><a href=\"#cek-konfigurasi-database-wordpress\" class=\"toc-anchor\">¬∂</a> Cek konfigurasi database wordpress</h2><div>\n</div><p>Sambung ke VPS Wordpress dan masuk ke direktori wordpress, konfigurasi database ada di <strong>wp-config.php</strong></p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-xml\">cd /path/to/wordpress/directory/\nsudo nano wp-config.php</code></pre><div>\n</div><p>Konfigurasi Database</p><div>\n</div><pre v-pre=\"true\" class=\"prismjs line-numbers\"><code class=\"lang